Combine greens, orange sections, celery, and green onion in a large mixing bowl. Set aside. Combine vinegar, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and vegetable oil in a small mixing bowl. Stir with a whisk until well blended. Drizzle dressing mixture evenly over greens mixture. Toss gently to coat. To serve, place 1 cup salad mixture on a serving plate and garnish by sprinkling 1 Tbsp. almonds over the top of the salad. Serve immediately.